{"tid":1700855,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當在比較偏嘅地方見到手足捉上車應對","createTime":"2019-11-08T17:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T20:35:21.000Z","uid":295317,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d056bd6370ecc39a3f2c5d71d57c1fa2f6f99bc9","tid":1700855,"uid":295317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:14:27.000Z","msg":"如果當時又無記者之類嘅人，只要有足夠人係周圍，可唔可以大聲9叫向狗嘅方向，指住自己手機，大聲叫:手足唔駛怕，我已經影曬你大頭(就算無都唔緊要)，亦有狗捉咗你嘅相，如果你之後有咩事，我就會公開相片！<br />\n意在減低手足被捉走後受害嘅機會，因為班杏家產狗做仆街野未必夠膽博你手機係咪真係有証據！<br />\n認同唔該幫推！"},{"pid":"bb182966b6d86c35806a0e1247184ed68746e752","tid":1700855,"uid":145496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"都係一個方法，不過啲狗可能會追你"},{"pid":"8075fa77a8139339c3a2fa654b014515d8cddcb3","tid":1700855,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"b00a54b6af17c44ad192794436777c4955451e8f","tid":1700855,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:47:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入黎rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06dd690a6270b9324e065a122d3c931b11e18a8d","tid":1700855,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:50:35.000Z","msg":"但平時有哂記者，影撚住開哂live都照打照強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440e262b553cf13b028a0a55b61f144f4d6dd9ed","tid":1700855,"uid":17802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:56:11.000Z","msg":"被挾嘅手足記住，永遠唔好放棄反抗。無論大嗌大叫，咬、抓、踢，扭嚟扭去都得。盡量拖長個時間唔好咁易比佢地夾上車，就算你完全肯定佢哋係警察都唔好咁順攤上車。一定要盡全力拖延/比其他人知到有事發生。你可能會因為反抗而受傷，被告多幾條罪，但係你喺無人知嘅情況下上咗車，你嘅結局可能係被凌辱至死都冇人知。所以一定唔可以放棄反抗！！"},{"pid":"5785b084e6260d5bab42db39a8fef14b2b3ac634","tid":1700855,"uid":17802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:58:47.000Z","msg":"見到有人被挾上車，同樣道理用盡一切辦法拖延時間等多D人過嚟，引起其他人注意。"},{"pid":"c207808b0a18c0b29ccf912b677520bb40f8b941","tid":1700855,"uid":252193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb182966b6d86c35806a0e1247184ed68746e752","tid":1700855,"uid":145496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"都係一個方法，不過啲狗可能會追你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:41:20.000Z","msg":"目擊健仔被鎗傷嘅FA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b7e29f08efe68fca5e3b67411a8e1e943bd971","tid":1700855,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69f4e2c64c5546f2c678b0f28af3e33086c742b","tid":1700855,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"[睇完前防暴貼士既你] 其實抗爭者係咪需要編纂一本勇武手冊？？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701002</a><br />\n<br />\n不如大家入黎研究下"},{"pid":"2aa2a61331fb9f0c0059e8210e32a7920c4f330c","tid":1700855,"uid":42978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20:01:24.000Z","msg":"大叫+反抗囉, 霎時間冇乜野可以做到"},{"pid":"9ac0637cb26de10f945c5e22fe41c9efe5d4a163","tid":1700855,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T20